CALM-Data-Generator — Authors and Contributors
==============================================

Project contact: calmdatagenerator@outlook.es

Authorship is documented here and in the project files (pyproject.toml,
CITATION.cff, README). It is independent of who administers the GitHub
repository, and the commit history remains the permanent record of
individual contributions.


Original author
---------------
Alejandro Belda Fernandez <a.beldafernandez@um.es>
    Created the library and led its development through version 2.3.0.
    Universidad de Murcia.


Current maintainer
------------------
Antonio Guillen Teruel <a.guillenteruel@um.es>
    Maintains the project from version 2.3.0 onwards.
    Universidad de Murcia.


Contributors
------------
Nasim El Arifi Ahmed <nasim.e.a@um.es>
    Author of scGFT Evaluator (https://github.com/nasim23ea/scgft-evaluator),
    the Graph Fourier Transform-based single-cell evaluation integrated into
    QualityReporter via the `use_scgft` option.
    Universidad de Murcia.
